HEADWORD: Transpierce
<hw>Trans*pierce"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Transpierced</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. &
